subject: internet doctor
body:
internet doctor resubmitted my prozac prescription as three twenty milligram pills my insurer will allow instead of the one sixty milligram tablet the insurer no longer supports and it costs less than three percent of the uncovered cost of the sixty milligram tablet

sungwon cho's videos "[i can recite any scene from disney's peter pan from memory](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=f3X8ifnz5cw)" and "[i can recite any scene from disney's peter pan from memory pt. 2](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-yMKYwdmggA)"
